    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚发现一个问题。CDN子图里的Edge节点和证书节点都标成了PLC_Logic类型，但Edge应该是EdgeNode类型才对。",
      "elements_involved": [
