    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "正确，ActuatorController是子系统名称，R53是里面的具体流组件。同样STORAGE子图是TelemetryStream类型，但里面包含EdgeNode和ActuatorController。",
      "elements_involved": [
