      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解，这是子图标签与内部节点类型的解耦设计。最终检查：PLC→HTTPS→R53→Edge→Lambda→证书→缓存→OAI Only→OAI→FILES，颜色和类型全部匹配。",
      "elements_involved": [
